room_title: Escape room "King Tut's Treasure" by Escape Modesto in Modesto
room_description: You and a group of treasure hunters discover the fabled hidden treasure of King Tutankhamun which has lain undisturbed for centuries. Once in the secret lair, the door suddenly closes behind you and you're locked inside with just one hour of oxygen remaining. Will you be able to follow the trail of clues and escape with the fortune or fall victim to the room like those before you?
